OL,3,C'It's a life sentence': Man jailed
OL,4,Cafter infecting HIV without telling her
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for recklessly
OL,7,Finfected a woman with HIV after he
OL,8,Fstopped his treatment and did not tell
OL,9,Fher about his diagnosis.
OL,11,FShe said that contracting HIV from
OL,12,FDavis is a "life sentence as I will
OL,13,Fnever be, or see myself, as the same."
OL,15,FLuke Davis, 31, was found guilty in
OL,16,FOctober last year of inflicting
OL,17,Fgrievous bodily harm on a woman who
OL,18,Fdescribed contracting the sexually-
OL,19,Ftransmitted infection as a "life
OL,20,Fsentence".
