OL,3,C'It's a life sentence': Man jailed
OL,4,Cafter infecting HIV without telling her
OL,6,FThe defendant, of George Street,
OL,7,FKidderminster, did not react to his
OL,8,Fsentence when he appeared at Hereford
OL,9,FCrown Court by video-link from HMP
OL,10,FHewell in Worcestershire for his
OL,11,Fsentencing hearing on Monday.
OL,13,FHe was jailed for four and a half
OL,14,Fyears.
OL,16,FDavis had initially taken his
OL,17,Fmedication after being diagnosed with
OL,18,FHIV in 2017, but disengaged completely
OL,19,Ffrom his care in 2019, the court heard.
