OL,3,C'It's a life sentence': Man jailed
OL,4,Cafter infecting HIV without telling her
OL,6,FHis victim, who cannot be named for
OL,7,Flegal reasons, discovered she was HIV
OL,8,Fpositive in 2021 after a routine
OL,9,Fscreening.
OL,11,FJudge Martin Jackson said Davis chose
OL,12,Fnot to tell the woman about his
OL,13,Fdiagnosis for "entirely selfish
OL,14,Freasons".
