OL,6,FThe judge told the defendant: "You had
OL,7,Fbeen told by the healthcare service,
OL,8,Ffollowing your diagnosis, that it was
OL,9,Fimportant that you used protection,
OL,10,Fcondoms, that it was important you
OL,11,Fwere open with any future sexual
OL,12,Fpartners.
OL,14,F"You chose to ignore that advice.
