OL,3,C'It's a life sentence': Man jailed
OL,4,Cafter infecting HIV without telling her
OL,6,FDavis's victim, whose statement was
OL,7,Fread to the court, said she felt
OL,8,F"physically sick as though my skin was
OL,9,Fcrawling" after being diagnosed with
OL,10,FHIV, which she described as "the
OL,11,Fdarkest time in my life".
OL,13,FShe said: "I struggle to love myself
OL,14,Fas I see this disease as a part of me
OL,15,FI can never get rid of.
OL,17,F"To me, it's a life sentence as I will
OL,18,Fnever be, or see myself, as the same."
