OL,3,C'It's a life sentence': Man jailed
OL,4,Cafter infecting HIV without telling her
OL,6,FIn a statement written by Davis's
OL,7,Fmother, she said that life had been
OL,8,F"unkind to him", including the fact
OL,9,Fthat his 13-month-old baby had died in
OL,10,F2017.
OL,12,FShe also said Davis had blamed himself
OL,13,Ffor bringing Covid into his
OL,14,Fgrandfather's home which caused his
OL,15,Fdeath in 2020.
OL,17,FThe statement continued: "Emotional
OL,18,Ftrauma led him down a path he never
OL,19,Fwould have chosen in better
OL,20,Fcircumstances."
