OL,3,C'It's a life sentence': Man jailed
OL,4,Cafter infecting HIV without telling her
OL,6,FAfter the sentencing, Giovanni
OL,7,FD'Alessandro, a senior crown
OL,8,Fprosecutor from the Crown Prosecution
OL,9,FService West Midlands complex casework
OL,10,Funit, said: "This was a reckless and
OL,11,Fselfish individual who has caused
OL,12,Firreparable damage by his actions.
OL,14,F"We hope the sentence imposed provides
OL,15,Fsome measure of justice to the victim
OL,16,Fand dissuades others from this type of
OL,17,Fdangerous and reckless behaviour."
